title: Honoring is dead
body:
I'm Fizz
{{champion:105}} "Hello, friends. Have fun! :)"
*Conversation with enemy Naut begins*
{{champion:111}} "Haha this is new. You're the first Fizz I've ever seen that isn't toxic!"
{{champion:105}} ":)"




No honors at the end of the match, and Naut and I had a pleasant conversation through the whole match.
